<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-ashamed-of">(be) ashamed of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>对……感到惭愧/羞耻</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You should be ashamed of yourself for telling such lies.
你应该为说这些谎话而感到羞耻。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You should be ashamed of your foolish behavior.
你应对自己的愚蠢行为感到羞耻。</p></div></div>